<abstract><t>This document defines a standard to extend Time Stamp Tokens with Time Attestations recorded on Distributed Ledgers.  The aim is to provide long-term validity to Time Stamp Tokens, backward compatible with currently available software.  This document update RFC 3161 [RFC3161].</t></abstract>

